{
  "texts": [
    "So, you should also apply it to those kinds of problems where it excels.",
    "So, I see a lot of people trying to apply AI chatbots to everything, also to things for which it is not meant, for which it does not excel, for which there are other solutions that are much better, much more efficient.\"",
    "Similarly, Managing Director P3 said: \"If it is not necessary, then we do not use AI.",
    "Then we use a dashboard, for instance.",
    "And well, you can see this as a decreasing footprint.\""
  ]
}